      • simulationStep

        public static boolean simulationStep(BagInterface<java.lang.Integer> heads,
                                     BagInterface<java.lang.String> work)
        Take one head from the headBag bag. If it is a final head, we are done with it. Otherwise put in two heads that are one smaller. Always put a chop into the work bag.
        Parameters:
        headBag - A bag holding the heads yet to be considered.
        workBag - A bag of chops.
